definition: to have/there is/there are/to exist/to be

sentences.english: Lipoic Acid is a powerful anti-oxidant and helps protect the brain.
sentences.chinese: 硫辛酸是一種強有力的抗氧化劑有助於保護大腦。

sentences.english: The body is brawny, limbs forceful, head round eyes, short neck little kiss long.
sentences.chinese: 軀體粗壯，四肢強健有力，頭圓頸短，眼小吻長。

sentences.english: In order to make strong shot, a player must be able to hold racket very hard.
sentences.chinese: 爲了擊球有力，選手必須將拍子抓得非常緊。

sentences.english: Finishing strong is one of the best feelings in racing.
sentences.chinese: 一個有力的撞線是比賽中最棒的感覺之一。

sentences.english: Beutiful photos and very powerful representation of a great Nation.
sentences.chinese: 漂亮的圖片，這也是對一個大國的強有力的展示。

sentences.english: Indra worried that this powerful sage would one day want to usurp the position of king of heaven.
sentences.chinese: 他擔心這位強有力的聖哲有一天會篡奪天帝的位置。

sentences.english: The critics have denigrated our efforts.
sentences.chinese: 批評家們受到有力的反駁。

sentences.english: Antibiotic therapy for diffuse cellulitis should be aggressive .
sentences.chinese: 瀰漫性蜂窩織炎的抗菌素治療應是強有力的。

sentences.english: The coffret provides strong added value to personal care products.
sentences.chinese: 與套裝提供了強有力的附加價值，個人護理產品。

sentences.english: At sundown, the strong cold wind has shifted from the southeast to the northwest.
sentences.chinese: 日落時分成，強有力的冷風由東南風轉爲西北風。

sentences.english: In addition, Chinese external medicine provided necessary support for treating ulcer after the surgery.
sentences.chinese: 中藥外用藥的應用對創面的癒合提供了有力保障。

sentences.english: Also provided a powerful safeguard for the gravity quay construction of large caisson.
sentences.chinese: 也爲大型沉箱結構重力式碼頭建設提供了有力的保障。

sentences.english: The power of the placebo effect is illustrated in the movie classic, The Wizard Of Oz.
sentences.chinese: 經典電影《綠野仙蹤》就是安慰劑效應的有力證明。

sentences.english: His shoulders were broad and strong, his hands were very strong.
sentences.chinese: 他有寬大強壯的肩膊，兩隻有力的手。

sentences.english: It is too strong and concise, not diffuse enough for a woman.
sentences.chinese: 那太簡明有力了，不象一個羅裏羅嗦的女子。

sentences.english: This technique, with its fast and strong feature, is relatively easy to use.
sentences.chinese: 跆拳道橫踢技術的動作特點是快速有力且較易使用。
